	<text id="ruskin_to_mother_august_13_1867">
	
	    <header>
	        <inventNo>1996L00330</inventNo>
	    </header>
	
	    <body>
	        <div type="text">
	            <pb n="1"/>
	            <opener>
	                <placeName><!-- match letter exactly, delete if unnecessary -->
	                    <rs key="Q5599500" type="place">Langdale.</rs>
	                </placeName>
	                <date when="1867-08-13"><!-- match letter exactly, delete if unnecessary -->
	                    <rs type="date">13th August 1867</rs>
	                </date>
	                <salute>My dearest <rs key="47637407" type="person">Mother</rs>,</salute><!-- match letter exactly, delete if
	                unnecessary -->
	            </opener>
	
	            <p id="p1">
	                <s id="s1">I've been writing a long letter to <rs key="76205504" type="person">Joanna</rs> - thinking every now and
	                then between sentences and it has taken <del rend="strikethrough">so mu</del> much more time than I
	                    intended.</s>
	                <s id="s2">- and I can only say, to day in this, that I'm very thankful to hear of that peace which
	                    came over you, and that I remain myself remain very peaceful and happy, and will write more
	                    tomorrow (though I shall not get your letter at <rs key="Q1025076" type="place">Keswick</rs> in time to answer
	                    it) - I go back to <rs key="Q1025076" type="place">Keswick</rs> because I left it before I had done, to show <rs key="8821113" type="person">Downes</rs> <rs key="Q390370" type="place">Windermere</rs> - if it is fine tomorrow</s>
	                <s id="s3">I shall go up <rs key="Q427283" type="place">Helvellyn</rs> again on the way back.</s>
	                <s id="s4">It was too cold when I was with <rs key="8821113" type="person">Downes</rs> <pb n="2"/> to see all I
	                    wanted at the top.</s>
	            </p>
	
	            <closer>
	                <salute>Ever my dearest <rs key="47637407" type="person">mother</rs>, your <expan>affect<ex
							cert="high">ionat</ex>e</expan> son</salute><!-- optional - delete if unnecessary -->
	                <signed><!-- optional - delete if unnecessary -->
	                    <rs key="73859585" type="person">J Ruskin</rs>
	                </signed>
	             </closer>
	
	            <postscript>
	
	            </postscript>
	
